The paper deals with image question answering, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) and Computation and Language (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel neural network architecture, which involves learning and predicting dynamic parameters, indicating that it may belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
